# Configure hostname, VLANs, and trunk links

━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

## S1

```cisco id="g9t1k4"
enable
configure terminal

hostname S1
no ip domain-lookup

vlan 10
 name DATA_VLAN

interface range gigabitEthernet 0/1-3
 switchport mode trunk
 switchport trunk allowed vlan 1,10
 no shutdown

end
write memory
